OL,7,FWhen Helen Hobbs receives a letter,
OL,8,Fphotograph, telephone call or message
OL,9,Ffrom a young person telling her about
OL,10,Ftheir achievements, she feels a warm
OL,11,Fglow of pride and contentment.
OL,13,FHelen has four children of her own but
OL,14,Fthese updates are from some of the
OL,15,Fyoung people she and husband Chris have
OL,16,Fhosted in their home over the past few
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,3,C'We take strangers into our home -
OL,4,Cthey're young people who need someone
OL,5,Cwho believes in them'
